-- Tate & Lyle Sugars Says Refinery Closed 3 Days a Week
-- B y   I s i s   A l m e i d a
-- 2013-05-26T04:40:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-26/tate-lyle-sugars-says-refinery-closed-3-days-a-week-correct-.html
(Corrects headline and first paragraph on plant closed in
story originally published May 24.)  Tate & Lyle Sugars, owner of the
London refinery on the Thames River, is closed three days a week
because of the European Union’s “protectionist policies.”  Tate & Lyle is watching as  Europe ’s agricultural ministers
meet in Dublin on May 26, the company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
